Foffonso's Chess

Simple chess game.
Multiple historical and local variations.

Can be played on the terminal, or with a GUI.
Can choose different algorithms to play against.
Local Multiplayer
Internet Multiplayer
Multiple boards and chess pieces for the GUI version.

Underlying chess framework.

Maybe make it possible for pieces to be in the intersections.

Variations:
Chaturaji
Chaturang
Courier (8x12 board)
Grant Acedrex (12x12 board)
Shatranj
Sittuyin
Tamerlane (10x10 board)
Shogi (9x9 board)




